  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Blanch the garlic by placing it in a pot of boiling water for about 2 minutes, then transfer to an ice bath. Peel and chop into small pieces.",
    "Sauté red onion in olive oil until translucent, add chopped garlic, black olives, and roasted garlic. Season with salt and pepper.",
    "Finely chop Romaine lettuce and mix it with sautéed ingredients. Drizzle with lemon juice for added zest.",
    "Serve cold as a light side dish."
